#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:1
msgid "Use and publish packages"
msgstr "使用与发布包"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:3
msgid ""
"MoonBit's build system seamlessly integrates package management and "
"documentation  generation tools, allowing users to easily fetch dependencies "
"from [mooncakes.io](https://mooncakes.io),  access module documentation, and "
"publish new modules."
msgstr ""
"MoonBit 的构建系统无缝集成了包管理与文档生成工具，让用户可以轻松从 "
"[mooncakes.io](https://mooncakes.io) 获取依赖、访问模块文档并发布新模块。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:7
msgid ""
"Before getting started, make sure you have installed [moon](https://"
"www.moonbitlang.com/download/)."
msgstr ""
"在开始之前，请确保你已经安装了 [moon](https://www.moonbitlang.com/"
"download/)。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:9
msgid "Setup mooncakes.io account"
msgstr "设置 mooncakes.io 账户"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:12
msgid "If you don't want to publish, you can skip this step."
msgstr "如果你不需要发布，可以跳过此步骤。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:15
msgid ""
"If you don't have an account on mooncakes.io, run `moon register` and follow "
"the  guide. If you have previously registered an account, you can use `moon "
"login` to log in."
msgstr ""
"如果你没有 mooncakes.io 账户，请运行 `moon register` 并按照指南操作。如果你之"
"前注册过账户，可以使用 `moon login` 登录。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:18
msgid ""
"When you see the following message, it means you have successfully logged in:"
msgstr "当你看到以下消息时，表示你已成功登录："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:20
msgid "API token saved to ~/.moon/credentials.json\n"
msgstr "API token saved to ~/.moon/credentials.json\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:24
msgid "Setup MoonBit project"
msgstr "设置 MoonBit 项目"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:26
msgid ""
"Open an existing project or create a new project via `moon new <PATH>`. For "
"example:"
msgstr "打开现有项目，或通过 `moon new <PATH>` 创建新项目。例如："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:28
msgid ""
"$ moon new .\n"
"Created username/myapp at .\n"
msgstr ""
"$ moon new .\n"
"Created username/myapp at .\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:33
msgid "It will generate template files in the path:"
msgstr "它会在该路径下生成模板文件："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:35
msgid ""
"├── AGENTS.md                    # Collaboration guide for agents\n"
"├── LICENSE                      # Open-source license \n"
"├── README.mbt.md                # README file with type checking support "
"for moonbit \n"
"├── README.md -> README.mbt.md   # Symlink for platforms that expect "
"README.md\n"
"├── cmd                           \n"
"│   └── main                     \n"
"│       ├── main.mbt             # MoonBit source file \n"
"│       └── moon.pkg             # Package configuration for username/myapp/"
"cmd/main package\n"
"├── moon.mod.json                # Module configuration for username/myapp "
"module\n"
"├── moon.pkg                     # Package configuration for username/myapp "
"package\n"
"├── myapp.mbt                    # MoonBit source file\n"
"├── myapp_test.mbt               # Black-box test\n"
"└── myapp_wbtest.mbt             # White-box test\n"
msgstr ""
"├── AGENTS.md                    # Agent 协作指南\n"
"├── LICENSE                      # 开源许可证 \n"
"├── README.mbt.md                # 带 MoonBit 类型检查支持的 README 文件 \n"
"├── README.md -> README.mbt.md   # 为需要 README.md 的平台提供的符号链接\n"
"├── cmd                           \n"
"│   └── main                     \n"
"│       ├── main.mbt             # MoonBit 源文件 \n"
"│       └── moon.pkg             # username/myapp/cmd/main 包的配置文件\n"
"├── moon.mod.json                # username/myapp 模块配置\n"
"├── moon.pkg                     # username/myapp 包配置文件\n"
"├── myapp.mbt                    # MoonBit 源文件\n"
"├── myapp_test.mbt               # 黑盒测试\n"
"└── myapp_wbtest.mbt             # 白盒测试\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:51
msgid ""
"`moon new <PATH>` generates a starter module with two packages. A module is "
"a  publishing unit that contains multiple packages. A package represents a "
"namespace  and a compilation unit, is defined by a package configuration "
"file, and includes  the `.mbt` files in the same directory."
msgstr ""
"`moon new <PATH>` 会生成一个包含两个包的起始模块。模块是包含多个包的发布单"
"元。包表示一个命名空间和编译单元，由包配置文件定义，并包含同目录下的 `.mbt` "
"文件。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:56
msgid ""
"Modules and packages are identified by a special path (not the file path in "
"the file system). For example:"
msgstr "模块和包通过一种特殊路径标识（不是文件系统路径）。例如："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:59
msgid ""
"username/myapp/cmd/main\n"
"─────────────────┬─────\n"
"────────┬─────   │\n"
"        │        │\n"
"        │        └─ package `username/myapp/cmd/main` within the `username/"
"myapp` module\n"
"        │\n"
"        └────────── module path. It also defines the package `username/"
"myapp`\n"
msgstr ""
"username/myapp/cmd/main\n"
"─────────────────┬─────\n"
"────────┬─────   │\n"
"        │        │\n"
"        │        └─ 位于 `username/myapp` 模块下的包 `username/myapp/cmd/"
"main`\n"
"        │\n"
"        └────────── 模块路径，同时也定义了包 `username/myapp`\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:69
msgid ""
"The template contains test files, documentation, and collaboration metadata "
"by default.  You can safely remove any template files you do not need.  The "
"following is also a valid MoonBit project:"
msgstr ""
"默认模板包含测试文件、文档和协作元数据。你可以安全删除任何不需要的模板文件。"
"下面同样是一个有效的 MoonBit 项目："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:73
msgid ""
"├── moon.mod.json\n"
"├── moon.pkg\n"
"└── source.mbt\n"
msgstr ""
"├── moon.mod.json\n"
"├── moon.pkg\n"
"└── source.mbt\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:79
msgid "Add dependencies"
msgstr "添加依赖"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:81
msgid ""
"You can browse all available modules on [mooncakes.io](https://"
"mooncakes.io). Use `moon add` to add the dependencies you need, or manually "
"edit the `deps` field in `moon.mod.json`."
msgstr ""
"你可以在 [mooncakes.io](https://mooncakes.io) 浏览所有可用模块。使用 "
"`moon add` 添加所需依赖，或手动编辑 `moon.mod.json` 中的 `deps` 字段。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:85
msgid ""
"For example, to add the latest version of the [moonbit-community/starter]"
"(https://mooncakes.io/docs/moonbit-community/starter) module:"
msgstr ""
"例如，要添加 [moonbit-community/starter](https://mooncakes.io/docs/moonbit-"
"community/starter) 模块的最新版本："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:87
msgid "$ moon add moonbit-community/starter\n"
msgstr "$ moon add moonbit-community/starter\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:92
msgid ""
"Moon also supports local dependencies. See [Dependency Management](/"
"toolchain/moon/module.md#dependency-management) for more details."
msgstr ""
"Moon 也支持本地依赖。详见 [依赖管理](/toolchain/moon/module.md#dependency-"
"management)。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:95
msgid "Import packages from module"
msgstr "从模块导入包"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:97
msgid ""
"The `moonbit-community/starter` module contains a `moonbit-community/starter/"
"rabbit` package."
msgstr ""
"`moonbit-community/starter` 模块包含一个 `moonbit-community/starter/rabbit` "
"包。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:99
msgid ""
"After adding the [moonbit-community/starter](https://mooncakes.io/docs/"
"moonbit-community/starter) module to your dependencies, to use the `moonbit-"
"community/starter/rabbit` package in the `username/myapp/cmd/main` package, "
"you need to import the package first:"
msgstr ""
"把 [moonbit-community/starter](https://mooncakes.io/docs/moonbit-community/"
"starter) 模块添加为依赖后，如果要在 `username/myapp/cmd/main` 包中使用 "
"`moonbit-community/starter/rabbit` 包，你需要先导入它："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:101
msgid ""
"// add this import to `cmd/main/moon.pkg`\n"
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbit-community/starter/rabbit\"\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"options(\n"
"  \"is-main\": true\n"
")\n"
msgstr ""
"// 在 `cmd/main/moon.pkg` 中添加此导入\n"
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbit-community/starter/rabbit\"\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"options(\n"
"  \"is-main\": true\n"
")\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:113
msgid "You can also give an alias to the imported package:"
msgstr "你还可以给导入的包起一个别名："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:115
msgid ""
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbit-community/starter/rabbit\" @alias\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbit-community/starter/rabbit\" @alias\n"
"}\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:122
msgid "Now you can call the function `hello` in `rabbit` package:"
msgstr "现在你可以调用 `rabbit` 包中的 `hello` 函数："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:124
msgid ""
"// in `cmd/main/main.mbt`\n"
"fn main {\n"
"  // println(\"hello\")\n"
"  @rabbit.hello()\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"// 在 `cmd/main/main.mbt` 中\n"
"fn main {\n"
"  // println(\"hello\")\n"
"  @rabbit.hello()\n"
"}\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:132
msgid "Run your main package and see what happens in the terminal."
msgstr "运行你的主包，查看终端输出。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:134
msgid "$ moon run cmd/main\n"
msgstr "$ moon run cmd/main\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:138
msgid "Remove dependencies"
msgstr "移除依赖"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:140
msgid "You can remove dependencies via `moon remove <module name>`."
msgstr "你可以通过 `moon remove <模块名>` 移除依赖。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:142
msgid "Publish your module"
msgstr "发布你的模块"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:144
msgid ""
"If you are ready to share your module, use `moon publish` to push a module "
"to mooncakes.io. There are some important considerations to keep in mind "
"before publishing:"
msgstr ""
"如果你准备分享你的模块，使用 `moon publish` 将模块推送到 mooncakes.io。在发布"
"之前有一些重要的注意事项需要记住："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:147
msgid "Semantic versioning convention"
msgstr "语义化版本约定"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:149
msgid ""
"MoonBit's package management follows the convention of [Semantic Versioning]"
"(https://semver.org/). Each module must define a version number in the "
"format `MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH`. With each push, the module must increment the:"
msgstr ""
"MoonBit 的包管理遵循 [语义化版本](https://semver.org/) 约定。每个模块必须以 "
"`MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH` 格式定义一个版本号。每次推送，模块必须递增："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:151
msgid "MAJOR version when you make incompatible API changes"
msgstr "当你进行不兼容的 API 更改时，递增 MAJOR 版本"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:152
msgid ""
"MINOR version when you add functionality in a backward compatible manner"
msgstr "在向后兼容的方式下添加功能时，递增 MINOR 版本"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:153
msgid "PATCH version when you make backward compatible bug fixes"
msgstr "在进行向后兼容的错误修复时，递增 PATCH 版本"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:155
msgid ""
"Additional labels for pre-release and build metadata are available as "
"extensions to the `MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH` format."
msgstr "附加的预发布和构建元数据标签可作为 `MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH` 格式的扩展。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:157
msgid ""
"moon implements the [minimal version selection](https://research.swtch.com/"
"vgo-mvs), which automatically handles and installs dependencies based on the "
"module's semantic versioning information. Minimal version selection assumes "
"that each module declares its own dependency requirements and follows "
"semantic versioning convention, aiming to make the user's dependency graph "
"as close as possible to the author's development-time dependencies."
msgstr ""
"moon 实现了 [最小版本选择](https://research.swtch.com/vgo-mvs)，根据模块的语"
"义化版本信息自动处理和安装依赖。最小版本选择假定每个模块声明自己的依赖要求，"
"并遵循语义化版本约定，旨在使用户的依赖图尽可能接近作者的开发时依赖。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:159
msgid "Readme & metadata"
msgstr "自述文件 & 元数据"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:161
msgid ""
"Metadata in `moon.mod.json` and `README.md` will be shown in mooncakes.io."
msgstr "`moon.mod.json` 和 `README.md` 中的元数据将显示在 mooncakes.io 上。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:163
msgid "Metadata consist of the following sections:"
msgstr "元数据包括以下部分："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:165
msgid ""
"`license`: license of this module, it following the [SPDX](https://spdx.dev/"
"about/overview/) convention"
msgstr ""
"`license`：此模块的许可证，遵循 [SPDX](https://spdx.dev/about/overview/) 约定"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:166
msgid "`keywords`: keywords of this module"
msgstr "`keywords`：此模块的关键字"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:167
msgid "`repository`: URL of the package source repository"
msgstr "`repository`：包源代码仓库的 URL"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:168
msgid "`description`: short description to this module"
msgstr "`description`：此模块的简短描述"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/package-manage-tour.md:169
msgid "`homepage`: URL of the module homepage"
msgstr "`homepage`：模块主页的 URL"

#~ msgid "MoonBit's Package Manager Tutorial"
#~ msgstr "MoonBit 包管理教程"

#~ msgid "Overview"
#~ msgstr "概述"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "[mooncakes.io](https://mooncakes.io/) is a centralized package management "
